{"tid":575041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「男友可以碰、爸爸也可以」哈哈哈　獸父猥褻國中女 唔駛坐監","createTime":"2018-02-28T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T10:29:34.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"caad6180784c059d06b0395fe431388cfda9cfe2","tid":575041,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"根據《聯合報》報導，單親爸爸阿虎(化名)獨自照顧就讀國中的女兒小秋(化名)，從老師那得知小秋在學校交男友，還被男友「隔著衣服摸胸部及下體」，阿虎暴跳如雷，不僅掌摑、拉扯、用菜刀刀面拍打女兒的臉部，甚至說「男生可以碰，爸爸也可以碰」，便抓她胸部、下體，又罵她是妓女、比妓女還不如，拿剪刀剪她的頭髮。<br />\n次日小秋到學校向老師吐露遭爸爸猥褻之事。台中高分院依強制猥褻罪將阿虎判刑10月，緩刑5年；並在緩刑期間，禁止對被安置的女兒實施家庭暴力、禁止騷擾、接觸、跟蹤或其他非必要的聯絡行為；遠離女兒的住居所、及學校至少50公尺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180228/1305357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305357&d=wzNEviSXu2%2Bb%2FbVpVe2lf%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=27e2a9a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305357&h=119aa6bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180228/1305357</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a47379cf1752632f4590b01ed3c0736ba5b94c","tid":575041,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"咁細個已經識講AV對白<br />\n不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41c39eb1a4cc3ac0e035e20865b56be2bd1f3e1","tid":575041,"uid":37933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"46a47379cf1752632f4590b01ed3c0736ba5b94c","tid":575041,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"咁細個已經識講AV對白<br />\n不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20